* '''Jesus the Splendour''' (Syriac: <span lang="syr" dir="rtl">ܝܫܘܥ ܙܝܘܐ</span> ''Isho{{okina}} Ziwā''). Sent to awaken Adam and Eve to the source of the spiritual light trapped within their physical bodies.
* '''The Maiden of Light'''
