{{mergeinto|Cunnilingus|date=May 2018}} The expression '''''to earn one's red wings''''' means to perform [[cunnilingus]] on a [[Menstruation|menstruating]] partner.<ref name="court"/><ref name="Hendley"/> The phrase is a reference to menstrual blood stains in the shape of a small bird's wings that are liable to form on the giving partner's cheeks during the act.<ref name="Hendley">{{cite book |last=Hendley| first=Nate |date=23 December 2009 |title=American Gangsters, Then and Now: An Encyclopedia |url=https://books.google.co.il/books?id=yQqSToDPO5sC&dq=earning+red+wings&source=gbs_navlinks_s |location= |publisher=ABC-CLIO |page=94 |isbn=0313354529 |author-link= }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Fritscher| first1=John |last2=Fritscher |first2=Jack |date=1973 |title=Popular Witchcraft |url=https://books.google.co.il/books?id=hiwvAAAAYAAJ&q=earn+red+wings+cunnilingus&dq=earn+red+wings+cunnilingus&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiYmurE0ZzZAhXEL8AKHR1KAMEQ6AEITjAH |location= |publisher=Citadel Press |page=131 |isbn=0806503807 |author-link= }}</ref>
==Background== [[Victor de Riqueti, marquis de Mirabeau|The elder Mirabeau]], in his ‘’Erotika Biblion’’ of 1783,<ref>A Wyngaard, ''Bad Books'' (2013) p. 61</ref> saw cunnilingus during menstruation as an extreme act, linked with the submissive worship of the [[Mother goddess]],<ref>J Fritscher, ''Popular Wtchcraft'' (2004) p. 190</ref> and by extension to the [[Black Mass]].<ref>G Legman, ''Rationale of the Dirty Joke Vol II'' (Herts 1973) p. 192-3</ref>
==Biker culture== The red wing patch was common among the [[Hells Angels]] by the mid-[[Sixties]],<ref>[[Hunter S. Thompson]], ''Hell's Angels'' (1966) Ch. 10</ref> and the slang term continued to be known among [[biker gang]]s in the 1980s.<ref name="court">''[https://books.google.co.il/books?id=lzBOAQAAIAAJ&q=earn+red+wings+cunnilingus&dq=earn+red+wings+cunnilingus&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiYmurE0ZzZAhXEL8AKHR1KAMEQ6AEINzAD North Carolina Reports: Cases Argued and Determined in the Supreme Court of North Carolina]'', volume 304. Published by Edwards & Broughton, in 1981. P.454.</ref> [[Gershon Legman]] saw the act/badge not only as functioning a [[Homosociality|homosocial]] tie, but also as reflecting a deep and primitive belief in the lifegiving powers of blood.<ref>G Legman, ''Rationale of the Dirty Joke Vol II'' (Herts 1973) p. 195-200</ref>
==Medical perspective==
Cunnilingus during menstruation is high risk for the partner performing cunnilingus because there may be a high concentration of virus in menstrual blood,<ref>{{cite book |last1=Pinsky| first1=Laura | last2=Douglas | first2=Paul Harding | last3=Metroka | first3=Craig | date=1992 |title=The Essential HIV Treatment Fact Book |url=https://books.google.co.il/books?id=Uz9KQRjWNToC&dq=cunnilingus+during+menstruation&source=gbs_navlinks_s |location= |publisher=Simon and Schuster |page=105 |isbn=0671725289 |author-link= }}</ref> such as [[hepatitis B]].<ref>{{cite book |last1=Newman| first1=Felice | date=1 January 1999 |title=The Whole Lesbian Sex Book: A Passionate Guide for All of Us |url=https://books.google.co.il/books?id=l5s4qoozxPcC&q=cunnilingus+during+menstruation&dq=cunnilingus+during+menstruation&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjgiq2o0pzZAhVMGsAKHddyBHgQ6AEIUjAH |location= |publisher=Cleis Press |page=241 |isbn=1573440884 |author-link= }}</ref>
